A grouping together of the moderate parties with us could build a bulwark against extremist agitation in the face of the crisis and further pad out the republic. [? if tower_r < 50 : This bloc does not itself have a majority, but if extended to include the opportunistic <span style="color: #a86b15;">**TNDP**</span>, it would. ?]

